{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01AY5vHpPJBgxHeMQ6ZGwS1H","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the issues:\n\n1. **`/app` vhost permissions:**\n   - `ops-user` has full `configure/write/read` on `/app` — this should be removed entirely\n   - `app-user` has empty configure (``), `.*` write, `.*` read — the configure permission is broken/empty\n\n2. **`/ops` vhost permissions:**\n   - `ops-user` has NO permissions on `/ops` at all — needs to be added\n   - `app-user` has NO permissions on `/ops` — which is correct, nothing to do\n\nRequired end state:\n- `app-user`: full `configure/write/read` (`.*`) on `/app`, NO permissions on `/ops`\n- `ops-user`: full `configure/write/read` (`.*`) on `/ops`, NO permissions on `/app`\n\nSo I need to fix `app-user`'s configure permission on `/app`, remove `ops-user` from `/app` entirely, and grant `ops-user` full permissions on `/ops`. After that, I should look into the client deployment crashes to understand what's causing them.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":862,"cache_read_input_tokens":28765,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":862},"output_tokens":36,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"90e31360-76f7-4e18-948d-416fd8566479","uuid":"63576314-db93-4b24-a764-b1351025d04b","request_id":"req_011CcaxqsTRhrDwaGrpocfEz"}
